   LEWIS-WITNESSES _ ATLANTA _ At least nine people have stepped
forward to say what they saw on the night after the Super Bowl,
when a fight in Buckhead led to a pair of fatal stabbings.
Baltimore Ravens football star Ray Lewis and two other men facing
murder charges. Here are the witnesses' statements, drawn from
various sources.
</P>
<P>
   Todd Whitehead was at Cobalt, partying with a friends, and left
around closing time.
