   He and  &UR; Miles Davis &LR; , for example, often converse. ``He just
seems as cool as ever,'' says Santana. ``I can smell him. Even on
the other side, there is smell. Like, when babies are born, there's
two smells _ one is chicken soup, which is the flesh, and the other
is lilacs, which is coming from the spiritual garden. The spirit
has a lilac smell.''
</P>
<P>
   Later, he said he could never be attracted to men. ``I mean, the
smell of men, it makes me sick. I'm not into men at all. ... Women
have a different kind of alluring smell.''
</P>
