   With: Byron Jennings (Henry Trebell), Brenda Wehle (Frances
Trebell), Kristin Flanders (Amy O'Connell), Richard Easton (Lord
Charles Cantilupe), Ross Bickell (Cyril Horsham) Graeme Malcolm
(Justin O'Connell) Pamela Nyberg (Lady Julia Farrant) and Jordan
Charney (Russell Blackborough).
</P>
</TEXT>
