<P>
   WEB-PHONES _ Not everyone who wants to use the Internet wants to
own a computer, but just about everybody wants to own a phone.
InfoGear Technology Corp. of Redwood City, Calif., offers the
iPhone, a telephone with a 7.4-inch touch-sensitive screen that can
bring consumers most of the benefits of the Internet without the
complexity, expense and space-hogging bulk of a full computer.
(Dayton Daily News). 13. WITH PHOTO.
