<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-12 20:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4775 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-ELIMINATE-CHINA-NEW-R     03-12 0036
